---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
const lastUpdated = "May 17, 2026"
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy" 
  description="Privacy policy for The Sawicki Group website."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">

    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-amber-700 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-stone-500 mb-12">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <div class="prose prose-stone max-w-none text-stone-600 leading-relaxed space-y-8">

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Who we are</h2>
        <p>
          The Sawicki Group is a real estate team operating under Coldwell Banker Realty 
          in the Twin Cities, Minnesota area. This privacy policy applies to the website 
          at sawicki-group-web-43343667811.us-central1.run.app and any future domains 
          operated by The Sawicki Group.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Information we collect</h2>
        <p>We collect information you provide directly to us:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-2">
          <li>
            <strong>Contact form submissions</strong> — name, email address, phone number 
            (optional), and message content when you submit our contact form.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>AI listing assistant conversations</strong> — questions you ask about 
            properties through our AI chat interface.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4">
          We do not use cookies for tracking, serve advertisements, or sell your 
          personal information to third parties.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">How we use your information</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>To respond to your inquiries and provide real estate services</li>
          <li>To answer questions about specific properties via our AI assistant</li>
          <li>To improve our website and services</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Third party services</h2>
        <p>We use the following third party services to operate this website:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-2">
          <li>
            <strong>Anthropic (Claude AI)</strong> — Powers our AI listing assistant. 
            Conversation content is sent to Anthropic's API to generate responses. 
            Anthropic's privacy policy applies to this data.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Resend</strong> — Delivers contact form submissions to our email inbox. 
            Form data is transmitted through Resend's email delivery service.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Google Cloud</strong> — This website is hosted on Google Cloud Run. 
            Google's infrastructure privacy policy applies.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Data retention</h2>
        <p>
          Contact form submissions are delivered to our email inbox and retained 
          according to our standard email retention practices. We do not store 
          form submissions in a separate database. AI assistant conversations are 
          not stored after your session ends.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Your rights</h2>
        <p>
          You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of any personal 
          information you have provided to us by contacting us directly at 
          jamesvsawicki@gmail.com. We will respond to all requests within 30 days.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Minnesota real estate disclosure</h2>
        <p>
          The Sawicki Group is licensed to practice real estate in the State of Minnesota 
          under Coldwell Banker Realty. This website is operated for the purpose of 
          providing real estate information and facilitating client inquiries. All 
          information provided is for general informational purposes only and does not 
          constitute legal or financial advice.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will update the 
          "last updated" date at the top of this page when changes are made. 
          Continued use of this website after changes constitutes acceptance of 
          the updated policy.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about this privacy policy can be directed to:<br />
          The Sawicki Group<br />
          Coldwell Banker Realty<br />
          Twin Cities, Minnesota<br />
          jamesvsawicki@gmail.com
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>